@startuml
title Fluxo: GET /books/{id}
actor Client
participant "router.book" as Router
participant "services.book" as BookSvc
database "SQLite DB" as DB

Client -> Router: GET /books/{id}
Router -> BookSvc: get_book(book_id, db)
BookSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM books WHERE id = :book_id
DB --> BookSvc: Book record
BookSvc --> Router: Book
Router --> Client: BookSchema (JSON)

@enduml
